{"tid":493850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"識左個日本女仔幾個月","createTime":"2017-12-09T03:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T17:38:04.000Z","uid":48126,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"666882c26fbac4b005efedb68e4db543e1d8ff8d","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"同佢係好偶然到荒謬既情況下認識。<br />\n佢讀緊大學，一個sem讀7科，加上其他free-riders，佢返學都幾忙，睇得出佢好認真讀。<br />\n<br />\n期間同佢每兩星期左右食飯睇戲、酒店high tea、去海洋公園，都係我約佢，出親黎氣氛都好好，佢會講好多自己野，包括近期生活。<br />\n如果同佢計劃撞期，佢會自己propose一個日期出黎，唔會不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n短訊雖然已讀已回，但我永遠無從得知佢生活，只有我單方面講自己野，問佢都係徒勞。<br />\n佢social media只有26個朋友，仲要not searchable，要佢add我先得，好明顯係謹謓言行既marketing page(佢讀商科）。<br />\n<br />\n小弟返緊工。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪收得皮，摺得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49119394fca089527890a7b15ebe912bedae3009","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac0c367040b26b95b4c5432336199e4a578830f","tid":493850,"uid":28720,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"會講好多自己嘢又無從得知佢生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01143740ed3312212550d0db4f73e03e1f1397e2","tid":493850,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"英文溝通？"},{"pid":"e6d7f5619591e3821441c50ba67cedd32136b0ee","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會講好多自己嘢又無從得知佢生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nText個陣就係咁⋯只有出黎先正常分享"},{"pid":"0bfa9b0be25a3b9b44e0c3102a31f06b5b57c5ff","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote