.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54d504ed6b6656203863e3fc6d4897ec0d6c7a1","tid":493850,"uid":28720,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會講好多自己嘢又無從得知佢生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nText個陣就係咁⋯只有出黎先正常分享</blockquote><br />\n既然見面都相處得好點解要喺虛擬世界去判斷一個人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11caca239f66967cc608a35f73f11d47d6bba7b","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"佢話而家無打算拍拖，收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMerry, merry Christmas"},{"pid":"b375d91ed2a1190ad9fab3010433d20f1d3c6459","tid":493850,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"點解一定要拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954b65729e8c36fe0e241ff3d766e4720849623d","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解一定要拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定， 想要拍拖既話，自問可以隨時都拍到。<br />\n但想和真心喜歡的人一起乃人之常情吧？<br />\n謝謝你入黎俾我取下暖。"},{"pid":"069f75fc95355425d15bd0454949116dd2fb244a","tid":493850,"uid":88695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e48743c3ed7f0e4fa1678414fb8c7f5a9a761","tid":493850,"uid":44050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n我慘過你"},{"pid":"ece45493b3f0a1cbaf76050a6a8aaab59f9a4ecc","tid":493850,"uid":48126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打<br />\n我慘過你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"4027d3051149bd686bb2c399452f779c3b6056a5","tid"